    "Proof of Activity (PoA) this approach combines PoW and PoS to validate transactions.",
    "The process starts with PoW, and then a group of validators performs PoS to place the transaction in the Miner's header.",
    "However, due to its high latency, PoA is not suitable for Internet of Things (IoT) applications and, therefore, is not an appropriate choice for eHealth. 10.",
